&lt;p&gt;If you’d like to learn more about the new Heroes, or connect with a Hero near you, please visit the &lt;a href="https://aws.amazon.com/developer/community/heroes/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt; AWS Heroes website&lt;/a&gt; or browse the &lt;a href="https://aws.amazon.com/developer/community/heroes/content-library/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;AWS Heroes Content Library&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt; 
